I am eager—viciously eager—to see "Home Life."2 It is like calling a version of "Fleurs du Mai"—"The Daisychain."

Yours very cordially

V. Nabokov





TO: JAMES LAUGHLIN

ALS, 2 pp.





Nov. 13th, 42

